# 5. Frontend vs Backend Logic

| Frontend / UI | Backend / Apex |
|----------------|----------------|
| Button click handling | Complex business logic |
| Displaying notifications | Fee calculation |
| Form input collection | Database operations |
| Showing attendance data | Validation and automation |
| User interface design | External API integration |

---

## Examples

### Frontend Logic
- Button clicks
- Form display
- Notification display
- User interaction

### Backend Logic
- Seat availability check
- Attendance calculation
- Fee processing
- Trigger execution

