# 6. Reflection

Modern enterprise systems use component-based UI architecture because it makes applications:
- Modular
- Reusable
- Easy to maintain
- Faster to develop

Reusable components improve scalability and reduce development effort.

Separating frontend and backend logic helps developers:
- Manage applications better
- Improve security
- Keep business logic organized

This architecture is important for large enterprise applications with many users and features.

